<span style="font-weight: bold;">Exhibition<br>
 </span>This project had its first public exhibition on November
19, 2004 at the opening of the new Cal-(IT)2 on the campus of UCI.<p>
It will also be shown at:<BR><ul><li>CHI 2005 in the new Interactivity venue</li><li>CSCL 2005 as an interactive presentation</li><li>SIGGRAPH 2005 in the Emerging Technologies program.</li></ul>
      </font></p>
