      <span style="font-weight: bold;">Future Work<br>
      </span>The team currently has collaborations under development
with Professor Lynn Carpenter in the Department of Ecology and Evolutionary Biology at UCI; with Professor Thomas Alspaugh and his research group in Informatics at
UCI; with Discovery Science Center in Orange County, CA; and with the International Wolf Center in Ely, MN.<br>
